\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {1}{\ignorespaces Policy-level monitoring on a safety island\xspace  . The monitor reads controller intent exported via cache-coherent shared memory (left path) and independently acquires evidence of realized actuation (right path) to evaluate temporal safety policies online. On violation, the island triggers a safety reaction within the FTTI\xspace  .}}{3}{figure.1}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:arch}{{1}{3}{Policy-level monitoring on a \SafetyIsland . The monitor reads controller intent exported via cache-coherent shared memory (left path) and independently acquires evidence of realized actuation (right path) to evaluate temporal safety policies online. On violation, the island triggers a safety reaction within the \FTTI }{figure.1}{}}
